WEBVTT

00:04.091 --> 00:06.484
Previously, on "The Village"...

00:06.528 --> 00:08.071
Who's Rashad,
and what happened to him?

00:08.095 --> 00:10.358
- I don't know.
- Gwendolina Ferrari,

00:10.401 --> 00:12.316
I'd like to ask for your company

00:12.360 --> 00:14.188
and a night you'll never forget.

00:14.231 --> 00:15.667
Dana's my first wife.

00:15.711 --> 00:17.278
We never technically
got divorced.

00:17.321 --> 00:19.932
- Are you still attached?
- Ava, I love you.

00:19.976 --> 00:21.543
I've moved on.

00:21.586 --> 00:24.459
I just want people to
leave me alone to fight this.

00:24.502 --> 00:26.287
Does that include me too?

00:26.330 --> 00:27.690
He didn't just
find out about us.

00:27.723 --> 00:29.246
He's known for years.

00:29.290 --> 00:31.031
- Katie, please.
- Let me go,

00:31.074 --> 00:34.773
or I will never speak
to you again!

00:34.817 --> 00:36.036
Hey, Nicky...

00:38.212 --> 00:39.735
I think you should leave.

00:41.000 --> 00:47.074
